                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "It is you. The founder, come down off the volcano to close the ledger by hand. Ashloam is the last field on my clipboard and you are standing in it like you own the ash. You did, once."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I have orders and a family paid in Company scrip and a fire behind me where the tower used to be. Do not make me do this. But I am going to, unless you walk back up the ash road."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Manager - late recognition",
