                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You are standing in an active yield zone. The family that mismanaged Ashloam has been transitioned to alternative outcomes, and the parcel now performs. Rows. Numbers. Ash and performance."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I run a string of fields off one clipboard, and Ashloam is the last line on it - the field the mountain keeps warm and the Company keeps counted. The last one you have to take from me."
